      "text": [
        "488 - وَ سُئِلَ: مَتَى تَجِبُ اَلصَّلاَةُ عَلَيْهِ قَالَ «إِذَا عَقَلَ اَلصَّلاَةَ وَ كَانَ اِبْنَ سِتِّ سِنِينَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.488 - He was asked : \"When does the funeral prayer become obligatory for a child?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"When the child understands the concept of prayer and is six years old.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
